section.def:
Association
                (救傷會) means the St. John Ambulance Association in
            Hong Kong which forms part of the Corporation;

Constitution
                (章程) means the Constitution of Hong Kong St. John
            Ambulance;

Corporation
                (法團) means the Hong Kong St. John Ambulance
            incorporated under section 3;

President
                (會長) means the President of the
            Corporation;
